about.summary: Plot on map projections (with coastlines and political boundaries) using matplotlib.

name: basemap-data-hires
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.0.8.dev0" %}
{% set commit = "ddf92f134f26aafd96228f43793586be1e52fd4d" %}

package:
  name: basemap-data-hires
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ commit }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/matplotlib/basemap/archive/{{ commit }}.tar.gz
  sha256: eed745099ba889e5e2c462316c8b58352e6edcc3df16a353b28a36e8ba6637e4

build:
  number: 1

requirements:
  build:
    - basemap >1.0.7
  run:
    - basemap >1.0.7

test:
  imports:
    - mpl_toolkits.basemap

about:
  home: http://matplotlib.org/basemap
  license: GPL-2.0
  summary: 'Plot on map projections (with coastlines and political boundaries) using matplotlib.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
